      <rules>
        <rule name="Master Strategist" id="bdf4-b116-4523-e808" hidden="false">
          <description>Any Eldar army including one or more Autarchs has a strategy rating of 4. While the Autarch is alive, you may shoose to add 1 to your rolls for reserves, regardless of whether he is in play or not (a roll of 1 always counts as a failure).</description>
