                    <characteristic name="Info" typeId="33e9-27bd-77e4-401d">Any time a Swooping Hawk unit uses its Deep Strike ability, it may place a single large blast marker centered on an enemy model anywhere on the table and roll a scatter dice. If an arrow is rolled, the marker scatters D6&quot; in the indicated direction. Work out hits and damage as normal.</characteristic>
