                <profile name="Veil of Tears" typeId="ae70-4738-0161-bec0" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="03b7-ec25-bb9f-b484">
                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Details" typeId="ad96-dfa4-b4ed-656d">A Shadowseer is a Psyker and always has the Veil of Tears psychic power. It follows the same rules as Warlock powers.


Any unit wishing to target the Shadowseer or the unit she is with must roll 2D6x2. This is their spotting distance in inches. If the models are not within spotting range, they may not fire that turn. The Shadowseer and her unit can always be ignored by the enemy for the purpose of determining target priority.</characteristic>
