              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">The Sword of Asur is a diresword that allows Asurmen to re-roll misses in close combat.
A diresword is a power weapon. In addition, if a model suffers any unsaved wounds from a diresword, it must immediately pass a Leadership test for each wound suffered. If any of these tests are failed, the victim dies immediately and is removed regardless of remaining wounds.</characteristic>
